						</div>
						<div class="box-content">
						<p>
						The complexity intrinsic in today’s events is growing exponentially. Meaningful, independent, third party validated data can make sense of this complexity and allow sponsors to choose events that will provide a sufficient ROI, making sponsorship a lucrative venture. Of importance in this regard is being able to utilize the data to differentiate between events and allow sponsorship of events to be dictated by pre-specified target demographic objectives and informed marketing decisions within industry segments. This will allow sponsors to feel confident about their investment, and allow for continued feedback as to what future sponsorship will prove valuable. 
						</p>
						<p>
Currently, there are conditions in the industry that impede the value sponsors gain from events. The EC helps sponsors access valuable data before, during, and after the event, allowing for an informed sponsorship decision. The state of the art EC Assessment Tool helps sponsors understand the important specifics of an event and allows the use of business analytics to determine whether the event is a worthy investment.  
						</p>
